{"tid":2223261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度邊境部署巡航導彈  目標鎖定西藏機場導彈基地","createTime":"2020-09-29T16:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T00:56:34.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d166d220d76f4ec9b96cf96ab00673fe2e46efe3","tid":2223261,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/2f2fc776-0260-11eb-b0f2-005056bff430/w:1280/p:16x9/ydd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.rfi.fr%2Fmedia%2Fdisplay%2F2f2fc776-0260-11eb-b0f2-005056bff430%2Fw%3A1280%2Fp%3A16x9%2Fydd.jpg&h=66810b6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網傳印度國產無畏(Nirbhay)巡航導彈模型 &copy; 網絡照片<br />\n<br />\n已經進入寒冷季節的中印邊境目前局勢仍然緊張，印度除加緊冬季備戰並運送大量主戰坦克與步兵戰車外，還在拉達克地區首次部署了印度國產無畏(Nirbhay)巡航導彈，可直接攻擊位於西藏的機場或導彈基地。台媒指這也是無畏巡航導彈研發7年來首次進行戰鬥部署，試圖以優勢軍事威嚇力量迫使大陸退讓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/tw/中國/20200929-印度邊境布防巡航導彈目標鎖解放軍西藏機場導彈基地\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F20200929-%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E9%82%8A%E5%A2%83%E5%B8%83%E9%98%B2%E5%B7%A1%E8%88%AA%E5%B0%8E%E5%BD%88%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99%E9%8E%96%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E5%B0%8E%E5%BD%88%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=bd76c240\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/tw/中國/20200929-印度邊境布防巡航導彈目標鎖解放軍西藏機場導彈基地</a>"},{"pid":"5f7f6bb30a16d1d1192957a69839deb8779871a7","tid":2223261,"uid":231583,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:17:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c567f28c17aaa4062518eec4f9844a3a6cc7d21","tid":2223261,"uid":103050,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:19:10.000Z","msg":"印度國產野得唔得架？"},{"pid":"aac92d291d30177eb32a396eefa8d918ab505771","tid":2223261,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7c567f28c17aaa4062518eec4f9844a3a6cc7d21","tid":2223261,"uid":103050,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score"